## How to Join During Live Sessions

1. Join the hub call at the scheduled time.
2. When the host shares the **Game PIN**, open Kahoot:
   - Go to the Kahoot join page (or open the app)
   - Enter the PIN
3. Use your real name (or your agreed team name) so scores are attributable.
4. Stay until the endâ€”final questions often decide the leaderboard.
